Bourne shell, Python, and other scripts for POSIX systems

This project has been tested on the following platforms:

+===========+===============+===============================+
| OS Family | Distribution  | OS Version (OS Ports)         |
+===========+===============+===============================+
| GNU/Linux | CentOS        | 7 (x86_64)                    |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | CentOS        | 8 (x86_64)                    |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Debian        | 10 (amd64, s390x)             |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Fedora        | 31 (x86_64)                   |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | openSUSE      | Leap 15.1 (aarch64, x86_64)   |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | openSUSE      | Tumbleweed 20200101 (x86_64)  |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Oracle Linux  | 7.7 (x86_64)                  |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Oracle Linux  | 8.1 (x86_64)                  |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Raspbian      | 10 (armhf)                    |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Red Hat       | Enterprise Linux 8.1 (x86_64) |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Ubuntu        | 18.04 LTS (amd64)             |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Ubuntu        | 19.10 (amd64)                 |
